{"/service/ndnp/okhi/batch_okhi_ham_ver01/data/sn86090528/00295864667/1920092401/0169.xml":{"full_text":"SECTION\nTWO\nTHE CHICKASHA DAILY EXPRESS\nSEPT. K 1920\nIF A.\nEDITION\nIBM VIE fyaa&l\n3 J Jr J)\nr Cl\".v.'i.?.i.ut\"v- J l\nStarts'\" at Chickasha, Okla., Saturday, September 25th, 1920\nGOE\nFOE\nYEAR\nBeginning Saturday, September 25th\nWe start our great Fall Drive. We have been receiving new Fall and Winter merchandise almost every day by freight\nand express, since July 1st and now our entire stock, three big floors 50x120 are filled to the brim with complete stocks of\nseasonable merchandise. s\nWe have set our goal at $500,000.00 for 1920 and we are determined not to do any less business than that amount this\nyear. We realize that in order to get volume, we must sell merchandise cheap and when you see our merchandise and com\npare our prices you will agree that we are offering lower prices on dependable good merchandise this fall than any other\nstore in Western Oklahoma.\nWe have taken advantage of our enormous buying power this year, for three big stores, by buying great surplus stocks\nfrom manufacturers who were \"stuck with the goods\" during th business depression this past summer. This- we were able\nto do only because of our great quantity buying and our ability to pay spot cash for merchandise. We are selling a great\nmany items for less money than the majority of competitive stores paid for the same quality of goods.\nIt will pay you to come from 50 miles around to do your Fall trading at The Dixie in Chickasha. If we can not sell you\nbetter merchandise for less money than any store in Western Oklahoma, we don't want you to buy here.\nREMEMBER THE DATE OUR GREAT FALL DRIVE STARTS SATURDAY, SEPT. 25TH.\nINDEX TO THIS EIGHT\nPAGE EDITION\nI'AOK ii .Moil's mid I.Joys Clothinj.\nBAG K ii .Men's and Hoys Furnish\nings and Work ClolliiiiK-\nBAOK 4 Ladies lints, (.'outs. Blouses,\nSkirts ami h i 1 d r i n's\nKeady-to-Wear.\nPAWK .r Ladies Suits, Dresses, Furs\nand Corsets.\nI'AOK (i Dry Goods, Dress Materials\nand Notions on Main Floor.\nI'AOK 7 Shoes for .Men, Women iuid\nChildren.\nI'AOK 8 Blankets, Comforts and\nBargains in the Bargain I\nJ\nBasement.\nPREMIUMS FREE\nBeginning\nSaturday, September 25th\nWhen our Great Fall Drive starts next Saturday, Sept.\n25th, we will begin to give tickets with all purchases of $1\nor more. These tickets always hold good as long as they\nbear our name (The Dixie) and they are redeemable for\npremiums in the Bargain Basement at any time.\nThis fall we will give as premiums Rugs, Dishes, Dolls\nand Glassware. It is not necessary to redeem your tickets\nriyrht after you receive them, but you may hold them till\nyou get enough tickets to get the article or set you wish\nfor.\nIt is remarkable what a store doing the volume of busi\nness we are can offer to its customers. Small merchants\nwill say that when you give premiums, the customer pays\nfor them hut we can prove in figures that the premiums we\ngive away pay for themselves by the increase they bring in\nour business. 4\nWe guarantee to sell you better merchandise for less\nmoney tha'n any store in Western Oklahoma and give you\npremiums free besides.\nM ON DA Y, NOV. 8 th\nis Dixie Day\nin Chickasha\nWe have set Monday, Nov. 8th as the biggest day of\nthe year. Every year we prepare one day which breaks all\nrecords in sales for the entire year. We go through the\nwhole store, select bargains from every department and of\nfer them for \"Dixie Day\" only.\nThe biggest day of the year at The Dixie in 1920 will be\nMonday, Nov. 8th. It will be the greatest business day ever\npulled off by any store in W'estern Oklahoma. We are out\nto break all sales records this year and if extraordinary\nlow prices all over the store for Monday, Nov. 8th only, will\nbring business, a record breaking day is assured.\nIt is too early at this date to announce the bargains for\nDixie Day, Monday, Nov. 8th, however, if you traded at The\nDixie last year on Dixie Day you have a fair idea of the\ncoming bargains and we promise greater bargains this\nyear than ever before. fl v\nstoq\nOF\nBRAND\nNEW FALL\nMERCHAN\nIf you have never traded at The Dixie inXhickasha you cannot conceive the vast quantity of merchandise we have gathered for this fall. Every depart\nment in the store main floor, second floor and the bargain basement is complete with great assortments to select from. We have always tried to keep\neverything the people came in and called for, -since we have been in Chickasha and this year we have out-done all our previous efforts. We can s a f c i y say\nthat our stocks are equal to any in the state as far as completeness and assortments go.\nWe especially invite people who live in small towns to cofrie and inspect our merchandise. We bring a big .city department store right to your door. You\nare sure to find everything you want here at great savings and it will cost you nothing but your time to come here as we pay. railroad fare or for your gas\nbill with all purchases of $50.00 or more if you live within a radius of 35 miles from Chickasha.","height":"26044","width":"20272"}}
